# Family Care

Family Care is an Android application designed to help users manage and access family-related information and services.

## Features

- Offline functionality
- Local data storage
- IndexedDB support
- Notifications
- User-friendly interface

## Download

The latest APK will be available in the Releases section of this repository.

## Installation

1. Download the APK.
2. Enable installation from unknown sources if required.
3. Install the APK on your Android device.

